    Read vcf

    read_vcf.Rd

    Read vcf

    Usage

    read_vcf(x = system.file(package = "balselr", "example.vcf"))

    Arguments

    x

    The path and name of a vcf file

    Value

    Returns a data.table object containing only SNPs

    Examples

    read_vcf(x=system.file(package="balselr", "example.vcf"))
